*fact(n as i64) returns i64
    if n <= 1
        1
    else
        n * fact(n - 1)

*mix(a as i64, b as i64) returns i64
    a * b + (a - b)

*main() returns i32
    a as i64 is 7
    b as i64 is 5
    log(mix(a, b))
    log(0xF0 | 0x0F)
    log((1 << 12) >> 6)
    log(2 pow 10)
    f as f64 is 10.0 / 4.0
    log(f)
    s is 'alpha'
    t is s + '-audit'
    log(t)
    i as i64 is 0
    sum as i64 is 0
    while i < 5
        sum is sum + i
        i is i + 1
    log(sum)
    log(fact(6))
    0
